                    <p>
                        <span>
                            founder and first coordinator, instructor at <strong><em>Martial arts karate academy NIT Hamirpur </em></strong>. A senior black belt in taekwondo and 2nd dan, black belt in karate, he has participated in various national and international tournaments including <strong><em>South Asian Hakuakai Karate Championship 2018 </em></strong> where he won gold medal.
                        </span>
